                "pour",
                "layer"
            ],
            "action":" cover the bottom of the prepared baking dish with about half the potato slices and diced onion. sprinkle about half the cheddar cheese over the potato mixture. arrange the pork chops over cheese layer. boil remaining potatoes and onion atop the pork chops. pour the sauce evenly over the potato mixture."
        },
